{"id":232952961,"title":"遊戲實況主工作?","content":"這是在104找到的 (各大找工作網站都有,以104為例)\n先上截圖\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/kHNtbsv.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/AG2gBmn.jpg\n\n先說說我目前的狀況\n我是念夜間部的 \n前陣子辭掉某外送的打工\n所以現在是待業 再加上其實本人對於實況是很有興趣的\n也算是一個夢想 本來就想當做興趣之一\n短時間內其實也不會找工時太長的工作\n剛好最近朋友傳這個東西給我看 \n我大概知道是要簽約沒錯\n大概要你一天至少開2小時這種 (這部分我沒什麼問題)\n不過如果有什麼業績要求 例如人數要到100之類的可能有點困難了哈哈\n\n\n有沒有這種工作的經驗談呢 \n感謝各位指教","excerpt":"這是在104找到的 （各大找工作網站都有，以104為例），先上截圖，先說說我目前的狀況，我是念夜間部的，前陣子辭掉某外送的打工，所以現在是待業 再加上其實本人對於實況是很有興趣的，也算是一個夢想 本來","anonymousSchool":true,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"6eeeafb2-9dac-4d81-ae4b-ffecf0ad4444","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-24T19:21:52.657Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T19:21:52.657Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":5,"tags":[],"topics":["實況","工作","工作經驗"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"工作","forumAlias":"job","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":5}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/kHNtbsv.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/AG2gBmn.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"6a818a8b-c6d2-4f1e-8ad5-d6162d9be704","url":"https://i.imgur.com/kHNtbsvl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/kHNtbsvl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/kHNtbsvl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-24T19:21:52.657Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T19:21:52.657Z"},{"id":"6a818a8b-c6d2-4f1e-8ad5-d6162d9be704","url":"http://i.imgur.com/kHNtbsv.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/kHNtbsv","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/kHNtbsvl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-24T19:21:52.657Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T19:21:52.657Z"},{"id":"8423a61c-42e1-4cb4-9e69-75f68bde4e57","url":"http://i.imgur.com/AG2gBmn.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https:/